OL,3,C'Better deal available' for Port
OL,4,CTalbot steel jobs, says Business
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FThe UK Government will press for "job
OL,8,Fguarantees" in return for taxpayer-
OL,9,Ffunded investment during talks with
OL,10,Fsteel giant Tata over the future of
OL,11,FPort Talbot.
OL,13,FThe new Business Secretary, Jonathan
OL,14,FReynolds, said he believes there is a
OL,15,F"better deal available" for the South
OL,16,FWales site and the steel industry as a
OL,17,Fwhole, as he confirmed negotiations
OL,18,Fwith Tata were continuing on Sunday.
