OL,3,C'Better deal available' for Port
OL,4,CTalbot steel jobs, says Business
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FTata has shut down one of two blast
OL,8,Ffurnaces at its biggest plant under
OL,9,Fits plans to switch to a greener form
OL,10,Fof production.
OL,12,FThe second blast furnace at Port
OL,13,FTalbot is due to be shut down in
OL,14,FSeptember.
OL,16,FUnions are opposed to the changes,
OL,17,Fwhich will lead to the loss of around
OL,18,F2,800 jobs, although Tata has argued
OL,19,Fits restructuring programme is
OL,20,Fdesigned to stem "unsustainable"
OL,21,Flosses of more than #1 million a day.
