OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FMr Reynolds described the situation at
OL,8,FTata as a "major priority" and
OL,9,Finsisted the approach is "not about
OL,10,Funderwriting loss-making businesses"
OL,11,Fbut being a "partner for investment in
OL,12,Fthe future".
OL,14,FHe told BBC's Sunday With Laura
OL,15,FKuenssberg: "There is more money
OL,16,Favailable for the steel industry under
OL,17,Four plans for government.
