OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,F"But that's about making sure we meet
OL,8,Fthis transition with the private
OL,9,Fsector together and recognise...it is
OL,10,Fa good exemplar of how we have to make
OL,11,Fsure that decarbonisation is not
OL,12,Fdeindustrialisation and we've got to
OL,13,Fdo that together.
OL,15,F"But there is a better deal available
OL,16,Ffor Port Talbot and the steel industry
OL,17,Fas a whole, I'm sure of that."
