OL,7,FMr Reynolds added: "I do want things
OL,8,Fin exchange for money we'll co-invest
OL,9,Fwith the private sector around jobs
OL,10,Fand technology.
OL,12,F"I think that's a reasonable way to
OL,13,Fmake sure public money is being well
OL,14,Fspent and I believe there are things,
OL,15,Fcapacities, the steel industry needs
OL,16,Fin future that could be part of that
OL,17,Fconversation and that's what I'll be
OL,18,Fhaving in the next few days."
