OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FHe added: "I'm going to make sure that
OL,8,Fjob guarantees are part of the
OL,9,Fnegotiation that we're having."
OL,11,FMr Reynolds said he would not put a
OL,12,Fparticular figure on the Government's
OL,13,Faims, saying: "Blast furnaces employ
OL,14,Fmore people than some of the newer
OL,15,Ftechnologies available, whether that
OL,16,Fis electric arc furnaces or what is
OL,17,Fcalled DRI, so there's a range of
OL,18,Fthings you have to understand.
