OL,7,F"But I absolutely agree with the point
OL,8,Fthat we have to make sure this is a
OL,9,Ftransition that works for working
OL,10,Fpeople and that they're part of that
OL,11,Fand you can't simply give money out
OL,12,Fwithout guarantees in exchange for
OL,13,Fthat.
OL,15,F"But there is a negotiation and I'm
OL,16,Fgoing to have to keep a little bit of
