OL,7,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,8,Ftold the same programme: "There's no
OL,9,Fdoubt that Labour coming in and the
OL,10,Fintent of what they want to do is a
OL,11,Fgood thing."
OL,13,FShe added: "My main focus is jobs, pay
OL,14,Fand conditions for workers so I'm
OL,15,Fgoing to either be seen as a critical
OL,16,Ffriend or a pain in the proverbial,
OL,17,Fwhichever they want to take that,
OL,18,Fbecause it's my job to make sure feet
OL,19,Fto the fire on this."
