OL,7,FMs Graham said the "devil will be in
OL,8,Fthe detail" when it comes to a jobs
OL,9,Fguarantee on investment.
OL,11,FThe Labour manifesto has committed to
OL,12,Fprovide #2.5 billion to "rebuild our
OL,13,Fsteel industry", with Mr Reynolds
OL,14,Fnoting this was "on top of" the #500
OL,15,Fmillion committed by the previous
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,18,FTata has said it would make every
OL,19,Feffort to mitigate the impact of the
OL,20,Ftransformation on affected employees
OL,21,Fand the local community.
